init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Most of the reincarnations are quite happy to be there, but some seem to be a little more fidgety.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start out as a child, living in a loving family.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You meet friends and have the typical teenage life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Just as you are getting to the climax of your teenage life, the movie stops.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They say that the movie always continues on until your death.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The current reincarnation will have no control over how the next moments of their life will be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They then all regret what they have done.
